        "htmlValue": "{{=&lt;% %&gt;=}}\n<div id=\"text\">\n  <h3>Component</h3>\n<p>\n  The HTML Template&nbsp;component allows you to write any HTML directly onto your dashboard.</p><p>You can switch from an HTML WYSIWYG view to the raw HTML, depending on the format you are most comfortable with.</p><p>It's called a template because it allows you to define mustache-style template parameters {{ and }}, and have those parameters filled in from a probe running in your app server.</p><p>Possibly the most widely used component, this gives you full control of your dashboard content and style.</p>\n</div>\n&lt;%={{ }}=%&gt;",
